Copy file data into a buffer.
The intent of this exercise is to just implement a buffer for operating on file data.
It may be entirely redundant, but that's fine. It's an exercise. :-)

Requirements:

- gcc
- kdbg

Setup:

> cd /path/to/project/root
> source env/shell

Building:

> build

Running:

> env/build/run size_of_buffer_in_bytes file_in_current_directory
# eg: env/build/run 2048 main.c
